### ðŸ§© Bonus: Integrate into `render_quest_tab()`

If `render_quest_tab()` is your custom function to render each question tab, you can modify it to also include the `uiOutput()` for the warning:

```r
render_quest_tab <- function(groupTag, id, question, options, descriptions) {
  tagList(
    # Your existing UI elements for the question
    ...,
    uiOutput(paste0(groupTag, "_warning"))
  )
}
```

Then in the server, just loop through all groups and assign the `render_severity_warning()` to each.

